translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  29,24,"Ke kaloku impendulo yabantu bakubo (uIbrâhîm) yaba kukuthi: “Mbulaleni kungenjalo mtshiseni.” Kodwa uAllâh Wamsindisa Yena emlilweni. Inene kuko oko kukho imiqondiso kubantu abakholwayo"
  29,25,"Kananjalo (uIbrâhîm) wathi: “Nina nithabathe izithixo ngaphandle koAllâh nazenza unxibelelwaniso lokuthandaza phakathi kwenu kubomi beli hlabathi, ukanti ngeMini yoVuko niza kukhanyelana ize indawo yenu yokubalekela ibe seMlilweni, yaye aniyi kuba namncedi.”"
  29,26,"Ke kaloku uLût wakholwa kuye (uIbrâhîm), wathi: “Inene mna ndiya kufuduka ngenxa yeNkosi yam, inene Yona nguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  29,27,"Kananjalo yena (uIbrâhîm) Samnika uIs-hâ’k noYa’kûbh sabeka ubuProfeti nesiBhalo kwihlumelo lakhe. Samnika nomvuzo wakhe kweli hlabathi, inene yena kuBomi oBuzayo ungomnye wamalungisa"
  29,28,"Kanti noLût xa wathi kubantu bakubo: “Inene, nina nenza ukungcola okungafaniyo nokwenziwa nangubani na ongaphambili kunani emaphakadeni"
  29,29,"Nina niya emadodeni nivale iindlela1, nenze konke ukungcola ezindibanweni zenu.” Ke kaloku impendulo yabantu bakhe ayizanga ibe yinto yimbi ngaphandle kokuthi: “Sizisele isohlwayo sika-Allâh, ukuba uthetha inyaniso.”"
  29,30,"Wathi yena: Nkosi yam ndincedise ngokuchasene nabantu abazizingcoli.”"